question.title: Slack App in socketmode is not starting and throwing "a request for an unknown workspace detected"
question.body:
Slack App started in SocketMode throws error as below -

Unsuccessful Bolt app execution (status: 401, body: {"error":"a request for an unknown workspace detected"})

Bot token and App token both are correct.

AppConfig config = AppConfig.builder().singleTeamBotToken(botToken).build();
    
SocketModeApp socketModeApp = new SocketModeApp(appToken, app);

Workspace is correct and verified with

AuthTestResponse authResponse = app.client().authTest(r -> r.token(botToken));
